*a)* Find the Norton equivalent ([`I_N`] and [`R_N`]) seen by [`R_1`].

[`I_N=`] [_____]{"$isc_display"} [`mA`]  
[`R_N=`] [_____]{"$ro"} [`\Omega`]  

*b)* If [`R_1 = R_N`], what is the power dissipated by the resistor?

